# --- Production zone files on wolfman live under /opt/bindcaptain/config/ (not this clone).
# This repo ignores config/ so laptops don't commit live zones by mistake. You still need a
# **Git backup** of authoritative zones: mirror wolfman → fluxmire (e.g. external/dns-bindcaptain/)
# or a dedicated repo; see fluxmire docs/plans/fluxmire-infrastructure-plan.md Section 3
# ("BindCaptain authoritative config: Git mirror").
# Configuration backups
backups/
config.backup
config.backup.*/
config/
config

# Runtime logs
logs/

# Test outputs and configs
tests/results/
tests/test-configs/

# BIND runtime data
*.jnl
*.bak
*.swp
*~

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Editor files
*.vim
*.swp
.vscode/
.idea/

